  "contentHtml": "<p><a href=\"https://substack.com/@lauralondon?utm_campaign=pr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Audrey London</a>, Los Angeles, to write a book on water in California.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/seyioluwasanmi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Seyi Oluwasanmi</a>, London, to bring Brits to SF to learn tech.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/thomashaferlach/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Thomas Haferlach</a>, Berlin, payments and compute layer for the long tail of AI apps.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/El-EnderJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Juan Ramón Egea Fernández</a>, Andalusia, tech.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://x.com/theodorspiro\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Teo Spiro</a>, Israel, AI and biology.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://amitav.net/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Amitav Krishna</a>, suburban Ontario, 14, quantum.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://jakeprokopets.substack.com/p/why-the-most-ai-exposed-counties\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jake Prokopets</a>, 18, Orlando, AI and labor markets.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wendiyan.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wendi Yan</a>, NYC, science and the visual arts.</p>\n<p>Luke Peoples, 15, Sydney, to edit the UI directly.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/malwina-lewera-668552337/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Malwina Lewera</a>, Poland, orbital space debris.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/wilhelm-hedenskog/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wilhelm Hedenskog</a>, 18, Gothenburg, Sweden, AI evaluations.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://nam11.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FAlexTPet&amp;data=05%7C02%7Ctcowen%40gmu.edu%7Cbbe16acaac824a09e21308dedb61858f%7C9e857255df574c47a0c00546460380cb%7C0%7C0%7C639189409084481586%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRyd